text: Cor Zegger (11 March 1897 - 5 January 1961) was a Dutch swimmer. He competed in the men's 1500 metre freestyle event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1897 births Category:1961 deaths Category:Dutch male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of the Netherlands Category:Swimmers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Swimmers from Amsterdam Category:Male freestyle swimmers
